---
layout: base.njk
title: The Consequence Layer
description: What AI actually changes. What nobody planned for. Examining AI's impact on systems, business, government, and society.
---
<header class="section section-dark blog-index-header">
  <div class="container blog-hero-grid">
    <div class="blog-hero-left">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">&larr; Rod Neufeld</a>
      <p class="eyebrow">Rod Neufeld</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title accent">The Consequence Layer</h1>
      <p class="blog-tagline">What AI actually changes.<br>What nobody planned for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-hero-right">
      <img class="blog-hero-img" src="/blog/Blog_Assets/blog_thumbnail.png" alt="AI Changes Behavior — The Consequence Layer" />
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section section-light">
  <div class="container narrow">
    {% if collections.posts.length %}
      <div class="post-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="post-card">
          <a class="post-card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">
            <p class="post-card-date">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</time>
            </p>
            <h2 class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="post-card-description">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <span class="post-card-cta">Read &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <p class="no-posts">First post coming Monday.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</main>
